" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT Plus</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="fbcf1024-1126-4795-9a58-4233d4f7dbee" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="109">Perfecto 🔥 entonces este template <strong data-start="35" data-end="63">no tiene Navbar separado</strong>, está dentro de <code data-start="80" data-end="96">app/layout.tsx</code> casi seguro.</p>
<hr data-start="111" data-end="114">
<h1 data-start="116" data-end="138">📌 Próximo paso real</h1>
<p data-start="140" data-end="145">Abrí:</p>
<p data-start="147" data-end="170">👉 <strong data-start="150" data-end="170"><code data-start="152" data-end="168">app/layout.tsx</code></strong></p>
<p data-start="172" data-end="193">Ese archivo controla:</p>
<ul data-start="194" data-end="257">
<li data-start="194" data-end="214">
<p data-start="196" data-end="214">El navbar flotante</p>
</li>
<li data-start="215" data-end="234">
<p data-start="217" data-end="234">El footer general</p>
</li>
<li data-start="235" data-end="257">
<p data-start="237" data-end="257">El wrapper del sitio</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="259" data-end="284">Mandámelo completo y ahí:</p>
<ul data-start="286" data-end="447">
<li data-start="286" data-end="307">
<p data-start="288" data-end="307">Cambiamos el nombre</p>
</li>
<li data-start="308" data-end="338">
<p data-start="310" data-end="338">Cambiamos el title del sitio</p>
</li>
<li data-start="339" data-end="376">
<p data-start="341" data-end="376">Cambiamos metadata (muy importante)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="377" data-end="418">
<p data-start="379" data-end="418">Sacamos referencias al creador original</p>
</li>
