/span><span class="ͼr">"Sistema para vender rápido con lector de códigos, impresión de tickets y control de productos. Ideal para kioscos/almacenes."</span><span>,</span><br><span>    img: </span><span class="ͼr">"/p3.svg"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    iconLists: [</span><span class="ͼr">"/re.svg"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"/tail.svg"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"/ts.svg"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"/three.svg"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"/c.svg"</span><span>],</span><br><span>    link: </span><span class="ͼr">"https://instagram.com/vertex.dev"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼl">// CAMBIAR</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    id: </span><span class="ͼq">4</span><span>,</span><br><span>    title: </span><span class="ͼr">"Punto Pádel — Turnero &amp; Reservas"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    des:</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼr">"Sistema de reservas con calendario, gestión de turnos y panel de administración. Pensado para canchas y clubes."</span><span>,</span><br><span>    img: </span><span class="ͼr">"/p4.svg"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    iconLists: [</span><span class="ͼr">"/next.svg"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"/tail.svg"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"/ts.svg"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"/three.svg"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼr">"/gsap.svg"</span><span>],</span><br><span>    link: </span><span class="ͼr">"https://instagram.com/vertex.dev"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼl">// CAMBIAR</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>];</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">export</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">testimonials</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> [</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    quote:</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼr">"Nos armaron el sistema a medida y se notó al toque: menos errores, más velocidad y mejor control. Siempre respondieron rápido y con soluciones."</span><span>,</span><br><span>    name: </span><span class="ͼr">"Cliente"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    title: </span><span class="ͼr">"Negocio local"</span><span>,</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    quote:</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼr">"El diseño quedó impecable y la web carga rapidísimo. La experiencia es súper profesional y ordenada. Recomendadísimo."</span><span>,</span><br><span>    name: </span><span class="ͼr">"Cliente"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    title: </span><span class="ͼr">"Emprendimiento"</span><span>,</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    quote:</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼr">"Lo que más valoro es la comunicación: explican simple, proponen mejoras y cumplen los tiempos. Excelente laburo."</span><span>,</span><br><span>    name: </span><span class="ͼr">"Cliente"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    title: </span><span class="ͼr">"Servicios"</span><span>,</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>];</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">export</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">const</span><span> </span><span class="ͼt">companies</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span> [</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    id: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span>,</span><br><span>    name: </span><span class="ͼr">"Vertex dev"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    img: </span><span class="ͼr">"/cloud.svg"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    nameImg: </span><span class="ͼr">"/cloudName.svg"</span><span>,</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    id: </span><span class="ͼq">2</span><span>,</span><br><span>    name: </span><span class="ͼr">"Clientes"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    img: </span><span class="ͼr">"/app.svg"</span><span>,</span><br><span>    nameImg: </span><span class="ͼr">"/appName.svg"</span><span>,</span><br><span>  },</span><br><span>  {</span><br><span>    id: </span><span class="ͼq">3</span><span>,</span><br><span>    name: </span><span c