t)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="c9fe77ae-e943-4c84-b3f3-04814971670f" data-testid="conversation-turn-44" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT Plus</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="6a877a77-efeb-4b94-8a7b-8188b19089f0" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="90">Dale, vamos con esos errores primero. Lo que te está pasando en esa captura es <strong data-start="79" data-end="89">simple</strong>:</p>
<p data-start="92" data-end="293">✅ <strong data-start="94" data-end="130">No están instaladas dependencias</strong> (react / three / @react-three/fiber / drei / three-globe)<br data-start="188" data-end="191">
y además TypeScript se queja porque <strong data-start="227" data-end="243">faltan tipos</strong> o porque VSCode todavía no “levantó” el proyecto.</p>
<p data-start="295" data-end="342">Esto se arregla en 5 minutos con pasos exactos.</p>
<hr data-start="344" data-end="347">
<h2 data-start="349" data-end="386">1) Primero: instalá todo (sí o sí)</h2>
<p data-start="387" data-end="469">Abrí la terminal en la carpeta del proyecto (donde está <code data-start="443" data-end="457">package.json</code>) y ejecutá:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="471" data-end="494"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-m5oiq452.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-m5oiq452.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼs">npm</span><span> install</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="496" data-end="555">Cuando termine, cerrá y abrí VSCode (o recargá la ventana):</p>
<ul data-start="556" data-end="607">
<li data-start="556" data-end="607">
<p data-start="558" data-end="607"><code data-start="558" data-end="576">Ctrl + Shift + P</code> → <strong data-start="579" data-end="607">Developer: Reload Window</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="609" data-end="665">👉 Con solo esto, <strong data-start="627" data-end="664">la mayoría de errores desaparecen</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="667" data-end="670">
<h2 data-start="672" data-end="765">2) Si siguen los errores de “No se encuentra el módulo three / fiber / drei / three-globe”</h2>
<p data-start="766" data-end="878">Entonces instalamos los paquetes que faltan (porque tu <code data-start="821" data-end="835">package.json</code> puede no tenerlos o falló la instalación):</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="880" data-end="952"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-m5oiq452.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-m5oiq452.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼs">npm</span><span> i three three-globe @react-three/fiber @react-three/drei</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="954" data-end="957">
<h2 data-start="959" data-end="1007">3) Si sigue “No se encuentra el módulo react”</h2>
<p data-start="1008" data-end="1035">Eso casi siempre es porque:</p>
<ul data-start="1036" data-end="1125">
<li data-start="1036" data-end="1066">
<p data-start="1038" data-end="1066">no corriste <code data-start="1050" data-end="1063">npm install</code>, o</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1067" data-end="1125">
<p data-start="1069" data-end="1125">abriste una carpeta equivocada (no la del proyecto real)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1127" data-end="1136">Solución:</p>
<ul data-start="1137" data-end="1239">
<li data-start="1137" data-end="1219">
<p data-start="1139" data-end="1219">asegurate que en el terminal estés parado en la carpeta que tiene <code data-start="1205" data-end="1219">package.json</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1220" data-end="1239">
<p data-start="1222" data-end="1239">y corré de nuevo:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1241" data-end="1264"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-m5oiq452.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none size-9 rounded-full px-2 py-2 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" aria-label="Copiar" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-m5oiq452.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼs">npm</span><span> install</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1266" data-end="1269">
<h2 data-start="1271" data-end="1346">4) Errores de TypeScript: “JSX.IntrinsicElements” / “any implícitamente”</h2>
<p data-start="1347" data-end="1442">Eso aparece cuando <strong data-start="1366" data-end="1398">TypeScript no reconoce React</strong> (por deps faltantes) o cuando faltan tipos.</p>
<p data-start="1444" data-end="1487">Después de instalar, si todavía te aparece:</p>
